* about

Alligator Eggs Lambda Calculator based on Bret Victor's "Alligator Eggs!"

Try Omega: 
https://propella.github.io/AlligatorEggs/#!/(%CE%BBx.x%20x)%20(%CE%BBx.x%20x)

* test in console

node lambda.js

* note

** peg syntax

name = [a-z][A-Z][0-9]+
var = name
abs = ("Î»" | "\" | "L") name "." term
paren = ( term )
prim = paren | abs | var
app = prim prim*
term = app

